description: This file contains the implementation of the CosaMTA class, which provides functions to interact with MTA-related hardware and system components. It includes methods for retrieving and setting various MTA parameters, battery information, logs, diagnostic triggers, and system statuses. The code also references external C functions for lower-level hardware interaction, and manages JSON-based request/response handling for a larger framework.
